  Minister of Federal Capital Territory, Mallam Muhammad Musa Bello, has mandated the use of face mask for every resident of the city in a bid to curb the spread of Coronavirus in the area.Bello's order followed a story by SaharaReporters on the poor enforcement of social distancing in markets across the FCT.  



